From: lixuyuan4 <lixuyuan4@huawei.com>
Date: Fri, 15 May 2026 14:09:54 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 09/12] qemu: arm64: remove CacheBindProcessHierarchy enum and
 location field, unify to CpuTopologyLevel topology

---
